萬個ON9仔睇佢<br />\n唔好彩既咪做極都咁霉 做多幾年都冇人識既話連老強金都儲唔到<br />\n<br />\n同埋大把YOUTUBER為左1日1片就走去開台打機搵題材<br />\n500蚊買隻GAME返黎打成個禮拜 <br />\n內容完全無內涵 見到棵樹又UP 見到架車又要講一講<br />\n有時為左賺錢又要做埋D cheap雞手遊宣傳 遊戲代理又貪平搵youtuber<br />\n有錢又有題材拍片班youtuber仲唔狗衝咩 求其對住部手機口upup叫大家一齊玩<br />\n呃鳩班小學雞以為入隻GAME就可以同自己&quot;偶像&quot;玩<br />\n實情係拍完片收完錢就del game <br />\n<br />\n香港Youtube搞到烏煙瘴氣完全係班小學雞同班垃圾youtuber搞衰<br />\n等於大台同班C9觀眾一樣"},{"pid":"7182df1cd8700ed6d33315083dd7fdecaf7e6665","tid":748460,"uid":186201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b22785e2e7b491d1df49a76a80c1d1fa06299716","tid":748460,"uid":97267,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T12:35:09.000Z","msg":"邊個嗯仔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T07:08:34.000Z","msg":"唔開名啦..冇人識佢啊<br />\n<br />\n12345<br />\n_樓有_仔"},{"pid":"1061a4c37630bbf0a17cc54b44ee451ce12e5065","tid":748460,"uid":174017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7182df1cd8700ed6d33315083dd7fdecaf7e6665","tid":748460,"uid":186201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b22785e2e7b491d1df49a76a80c1d1fa06299716","tid":748460,"uid":97267,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T12:35:09.000Z","msg":"邊個嗯仔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T07:08:34.000Z","msg":"唔開名啦..冇人識佢啊<br />\n<br />\n12345<br />\n_樓有_仔"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T07:24:42.000Z","msg":"原來講緊佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n條友好似好恨做明星咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9f77bf521c33ea90dec209bbc70326e46c3e46d","tid":748460,"uid":53254,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T07:28:24.000Z","msg":"我想要~~ 雙層~~~<br />\n收看次數：100,160"}]}